column3: “Fantastic smoke. This is one of the best strains I've smoked, and I've smoked two to three dozen. This is the baseline IMHO for other cannabis strains. Powerful psychedelic trance state like what Master Kush does. Narcotic-like stone like Afghani, but less body and more cerebral - no tiredness. Did I eat two shrooms or smoke a bowl of Humdinger? You might not be able to tell the difference. Never had Sour Bubble, but...”
